{"origin":33156,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Mithaq: Allah takes covenant from children of Adam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 17, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah took the covenant from the loins of Adam at Arafat, bringing forth from his backbone every seed that he would sow. He scattered them before him and then He spoke to them as they stood before Him,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15674,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/14\/no-fasting-eid-fitr-adha-tashriq\/","url_meta":{"origin":33156,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Eids: Days of Eid are celebrations, not for fasting","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Uqbah ibn 'Amir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe day of Arafat, the day of sacrifice, and the three following days of al-Tashriq\u00a0are celebrations for the people of Islam. They are days of eating and drinking.\u201d Al-Tirmidhi said, \"The people of knowledge acted\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":33078,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/08\/03\/barakah-dhul-hijjah-arafat\/","url_meta":{"origin":33156,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on \u2018Arafah: Blessings of Dhul-Hijjah, day of Arafat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 3, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cNo days are better to Allah than the first ten days of Dhul-Hijjah.\u201d A man said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, are they better or time spent waging jihad in the way of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThey\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20945,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/09\/23\/best-dua-yawm-arafah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33156,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on &#8216;Arafah: Best supplication on day of Arafat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 23, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best supplication is that which is made on the day of Arafat. The best of it is what was said by myself and the Prophets before me, 'There is no God but Allah alone, without any\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":23690,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2016\/09\/06\/hajj-itself-is-arafah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33156,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Arafat: Hajj culminates in day of &#8216;Arafah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 6, 2016","format":false,"excerpt":"'Abdu Rahman ibn Ya\u2019mar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe Hajj is Arafat. Whoever reaches the night of Arafat before the rising of the sun at dawn the next day, he has completed his pilgrimage.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 3016 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15670,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/08\/14\/fasting-or-not-arafah\/","url_meta":{"origin":33156,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Hajj: Fasting or not on the day of Arafat","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: I have performed the Hajj pilgrimage with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he did not fast during Arafat. I performed it with Abu Bakr and he did not fast, with Umar and he did not fast, and with Uthman and he did not\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33156","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=33156"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/33156\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=33156"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=33156"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=33156"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}